rfiles/images/2014-3-19/20143191350103111.jpg\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" tangram_guid=\"TANGRAM_23\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; width: 500px; height: 375px; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /></span></p>\r\n<p sizcache=\"2\" sizset=\"175\">　　</p>\r\n<p sizcache=\"2\" sizset=\"175\">迅扬S607机箱采用了非常合理的内部五金结构，可以容纳MicroATX主板和刀板显卡的使用。这款机箱的尺寸仅为391&times;100&times;306mm，散热性能优秀，并提供机箱活动支架。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" jquery1364290708968=\"20\" sizcache=\"4\" sizset=\"5\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" jquery1364290708968=\"20\" sizcache=\"4\" sizset=\"5\"><span class=\"pro_pic_rel\" jquery1364290708968=\"24\" style=\"width: 502px; display: inline\"><img title=\" \" alt=\" \" src=\"http://itdinghuo.com/ckeditor/userfiles/images/2014-3-19/20143191350179015.jpg\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" tangram_guid=\"TANGRAM_24\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; width: 500px; height: 375px; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /></span></p>\r\n<p sizcache=\"2\" sizset=\"178\">　　</p>\r\n<p sizcache=\"2\" sizset=\"178\">迅扬S607标配了原生19针原生USB3.0，不仅为大家提供更快的传输速度，还可以为手机等电子产品更快的进行充电，帮助大家节省一定的时间。</p>\r\n<center sizcache=\"2\" sizset=\"179\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\" sizcache=\"2\" sizset=\"179\" style=\"width: 375pt; background: #a2c7e1\">\r\n    <tbody sizcache=\"2\" sizset=\"179\">\r\n        <tr sizcache=\"2\" sizset=\"179\">\r\n            <td height=\"30\" colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" sizcache=\"2\" sizset=\"179\" style=\"border-bottom-color: #d0d0d0; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; border-top-color: #d0d0d0; padding-left: 2.25pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; background: #e1e9ff; border-right-color: #d0d0d0; font-size: 12px; border-left-color: #d0d0d0; padding-top: 2.25pt\">迅扬 小蜜蜂S607</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td bgcolor=\"#f7f9ff\" width=\"30%\" align=\"center\" style=\"border-